[30;1m56 | [0m[35m```[0m
[30;1m57 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m58 | [0m[35mThis should only ever be done at the top-level application layer, in[0m

[30;1m60 | [0m[35mshould **not** do this in a library, because it can cause unexpected[0m
[30;1m61 | [0m[35mdelays in other parts of the program.[0m
